data.title: Hey Girl (song)
data.meta_description: "Hey Girl" is a song written by Lady Gaga and Florence Welch, of Florence + the Machine, for Gaga's fifth studio album Joanne. Lady Gaga performed a small snippet of the song October 5th, 2016, during her interview on 102.7 KIIS FM. The track is the only collaboration on the album. Rumors about...
